These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, horror, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, country, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, american, brazilian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, roller, skateboard
1. the american is the fan of ambient##1
2. the brazilian is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching family movies##2
3. the american is the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the fan of classical is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | family   | musical  | horror  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | ambient    | classical      | country    |
| Nationality   | spanish | american | brazilian | japanese |
| Transport     | skateboard  | subway       | motorbike    | roller     |

