.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, traveling, collecting, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, thriller, documentary, superhero
4 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, hedgehog, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, skiing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching superhero movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
7. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
9. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography | traveling    | collecting  | filmmaking    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | thriller  | superhero  | documentary |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | hedgehog       | hamster      | snake       |
| Sport         | surfing    | biathlon | skiing | climbing |

