.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, pear, asparagus, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, skydiving, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, nurse, accountant, journalist
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, car, van
1. the accountant is the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the nurse is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person eating banana is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person eating asparagus and the nurse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pear | asparagus     | banana   | raspberry     |
| Hobby       | card-games   | video-games   | skydiving | filmmaking |
| Job         | electrician   | accountant | journalist       | nurse    |
| Transport   | car    | jet-ski | bike  | van    |

