 3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person watching family movies is the journalist##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the analyst is between the owner of the cat and the bartender##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | pilot  | bartender | analyst     | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | superhero  | comedy | family       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig       | mouse    | goat      | cat           |
| Sport         | golf | snowboarding   | badminton   | cycling         |

