 4. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the firefighter is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 8. the coach is the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person eating cherry is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person watching disaster movies##2
10. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
