 7. the australian is the person driving the roller##1
 8. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the french is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
