There 4 different types of food: apricot, cherry, banana, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, baking, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, fish, mouse
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person eating apricot is the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating apricot and the person eating banana##2
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person eating apricot and the person eating banana##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | water    | 7up    | coffee      | milk |
| Food       | apricot        | raspberry       | banana       | cherry     |
| Hobby      | baking | gardening | skydiving | card-games        |
| Pet        | goldfish       | mouse     | fish         | guinea-pig           |

