 3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 5. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating eggplant##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the person driving the tram##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
